title: Texas High Schoolers Must Retake SATs After Tests Fly Off UPS Truck
description: Seniors who sat for the SATs last month at El Paso High School will have to retake the test after many of the sheets with their answers were scattered on the street.
dc:creator: Claire Fahy
media:description: Students were called to a meeting last week and told the SAT tests they had taken on Oct. 27 had flown off the UPS truck that was transporting them.
